name_pretty: Google Cloud Hosted Marketplace V2 API
ruby-cloud-description: google-cloud-hosted-marketplace-v2 is the official client library for the Google Cloud Hosted Marketplace V2 API. Note that google-cloud-hosted-marketplace-v2 is a version-specific client library. For most uses, we recommend installing the main client library google-cloud-hosted-marketplace instead. See the readme for more details.
